quran[24{c,v,t}:
26,160,loot ki qoum ne Rasolo-n ko jhatlaya
26,161,"yaad karo jabkay un ke bhai loot ne un se kaha tha"" kya tum drtay nahi ?"
26,162,mein tumahray liye aik amanat daar rasool hon
26,163,lehaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
26,164,"mein is kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi hon, mera ajar to rab alameen ke zimma hai"
26,165,kya tum duniya ki makhlooq mein se Mardon ke paas jatay ho
26,166,"aur tumhari biwion mein tumahray rab ne tumahray liye jo kuch peda kya hai usay chore dete ho? balkay tum log to hadd se hi guzar gay ho """
26,167,"unhon ne kaha “اے loot,"" agar to inn baton se baz nah aaya to jo log hamari bustiyon se nikalay gay hain unn mein to bhi shaamil ho kar rahay ga """
26,168,"is ne kaha"" tumahray krtoton par jo log کڑھ rahay hain mein unn mein shaamil hon"
26,169,"ae parvar-digaar, mujhe aur mere ahal o Ayal ko un ki bad kardatyon se nijaat day """
26,170,aakhir kaar hum ne usay aur is ke sab ahal o Ayal ko bacha liya
26,171,bajuz aik budiya ke jo peechay reh jaane walon mein thi
26,172,phir baqi mandah logon ko hum ne tabah kar diya
26,173,"aur un par brsayi aik barsaat, barri hi burii barish thi jo unn dry jaane walon par nazil hui"
26,174,"yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai, magar inn mein se aksar maan-ne walay nahi"
26,175,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
26,176,ashaab الایکہul aikah ne Rasolo-n ko jhutlaya
26,177,"yaad karo jabkay Shoiab ne un se kaha tha"" kya tum drtay nahi ?"
26,178,mein tumahray liye aik amanat daar rasool hon
26,179,lehaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
26,180,mein is kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi hon mera ajar to rab alameen ke zimma hai
26,181,pemanay theek bharo aur kisi ko ghata nah do
26,182,sahih traazo se tulo
26,183,aur logon ko un ki cheeze kam nah do zameen mein fasaad nah pheilatay phiro
